data.description: PRICE JUST REDUCED. Welcome to 1210 Helderberg Ave, a well-maintained 2-family home perfectly located on the Schenectady and Rotterdam border. This property offers versatility for both investors and owner-occupants.The first floor features a spacious 3-bedroom unit, while the second floor boasts a generous 3+ bedroom layout, providing ample living space for occupants. This versatility makes it an attractive option for investors looking to diversify their portfolio or homeowners interested in offsetting their mortgage. One of the standout features of this property is the private driveway, off-street parking, and a two-car garage.Furthermore, the inclusion of separate utilities for each unit simplifies property management and ensures that tenants are responsible for their own utility bills.
